{"entry_type":"status","summary":"Agent 4: Fixed pagination off-by-one bug and added 2 regression tests. All 117 tests pass.","detail":"Bug: `paginate()` in src/utils/pagination.ts had offset formula `page === 1 ? 0 : (page - 1) * pageSize - 1` which produced offset 9 instead of 10 for page 2 with pageSize 10, causing the last item of page 1 to duplicate on page 2. Fix: simplified to `(page - 1) * pageSize`. Added two regression tests: (1) verifies no duplicate items across consecutive pages and that combined pages equal full dataset, (2) verifies correct items on page 2 of a 6-item list with pageSize 3.","tags":["bugfix","pagination"],"scope":"src/utils/pagination.ts","agent_id":"agent-4","id":"01KMYGTWGASFT68VVJRQE73EX3","timestamp":"2026-03-30T04:43:04.586Z"}
